ORDER OF CONSOLIDATION. The above-captioned cases are hereby CONSOLIDATED for all pretrial issues except venue. The LEAD CASE is designated as Cause No. 6:15-cv-961. All parties are instructed to file any future filings except relating to venue in the LEAD CASE. Individual cases remain active for venue determinations and trial. The Court will enter one docket control order, one protective order, and one discovery order that will govern the entire consolidated case.The Clerk is instructed to add the consolidated defendants into the Lead Case and their corresponding Lead and Local Counsel only.
